column4: "dougmck@pipeline.com.au. This was recorded at least 3 times by Bill Evans (once with Tony Bennet) - usually as done here - beginning rubato - then in tempo - then rubato to finish.\012"
"LH plays Root and a rising 5th bar by bar beginning on the b5 thru 5th thru #5th thru 6th to b7th on the fifth bar of the song"
"A whole step/half step diminished scale over the Bb chords"
"'So what' type chords descend with the  top note playing down a Bb scale."
